script how to use kcachegrind to view the results.

author: kfogel
msg: Continue work on issue #1510: marshal vendor head revision information
to the point of commit.
* tools/cvs2svn/cvs2svn.py
(DEFAULT_BRANCHES_DB): Document that CVS paths are relative now.
(CollectData.define_revision): Use relative CVS paths.  Add some
more comments.
(CollectData.set_revision_info): Handle non-imported 1.1's with a
special case and a quote from Raiders of the Lost Ark.
(is_trunk_vendor_revision): New function.
(Commit.commit): Notice if this is a trunk vendor revision, but just
pass for now if it is.
